---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Copyright & Abuse Policy — Super Downloads" description="Copyright and Abuse Policy for Super Downloads.">
  <div class="legal">
    <a href="/" class="back">&larr; Back</a>
    <h1>Copyright &amp; Abuse Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: July 16, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. What Super Downloads Is</h2>
    <p>Super Downloads is a desktop tool that helps video editors save video for their offline editing workflow. It is designed for downloading your own content, licensed content, Creative Commons material, public domain works, and content you are otherwise authorized to download.</p>

    <h2>2. We Do Not Host Content</h2>
    <p>Super Downloads does not host, store, or distribute any copyrighted content. The App runs entirely on the user's computer, and downloads travel directly from the source platform to the user's device. No content passes through our servers, and we have no access to, or record of, what users download.</p>

    <h2>3. Respect for Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>We respect the intellectual property rights of creators and rights holders. Our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> require users to download only content they own or are authorized to download, and prohibit any circumvention of DRM or technical access controls.</p>

    <h2>4. Contact for Rights Holders</h2>
    <p>If you are a rights holder and believe any material on this website (superdownloads.app) infringes your rights — for example, imagery, text, or promotional material we publish ourselves — contact us at <a href="mailto:support@superdownloads.app">support@superdownloads.app</a> with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Identification of the work you believe is infringed</li>
      <li>The URL on this website where the material appears</li>
      <li>Your contact information and your relationship to the work</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>We will acknowledge legitimate rights-holder inquiries promptly — normally within 7 days — and will remove or correct any material on our own website that infringes third-party rights. Because we do not host or have access to user downloads, we cannot remove content stored on users' devices, but we take reports of misuse of the App seriously and may terminate licenses used in violation of our Terms.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@superdownloads.app">support@superdownloads.app</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
  }

  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
</style>
